<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1037850" n="1"/> 
<opener><lb/><salute><abbr>F.</abbr> <abbr>C.</abbr> Amico suo <abbr>pl.</abbr> colendo <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs type="person">N. B.</rs></salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Salvus et incolumis, Deo sit gratia, <date>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terito die Lun<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></date> in hanc <rs type="place">Urbem</rs> veni, et postridie hospitium
<lb/>sumsi apud certam quandam Matronam <rs type="person">Charlottam</rs> non ita procul ab <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dibus Sarasin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, in qui<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>bus habitat <rs type="person">Raillardus</rs> noster, et in quibus ipse co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>oratus essem, si camera aliqua vacua fu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>isset; citius quidem te adventus mei certiorem fecissem, si licuisset, nunc autem co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odam ad te
<lb/>scribendi occasionem mihi suppeditat <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Morellus</rs> <rs type="person">Feschii</rs> affinis, quem socium itineris habui, et
<lb/>qui <date>crastina die</date> <rs type="place">Basileam</rs> reversurus me rogavit, nunquid amicis significandum haberem;
<lb/>illum ergo <rs type="letter">literis</rs> ad <rs type="person">Feschium</rs> onerare eisque aliquas ad te includere optimum esse duxi.
<lb/>Ecce autem dum me scriptioni accingo tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Raillardo</rs> redduntur <rs type="letter">liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, quas quan<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>to cum gaudio aperui tanta cum tristitia perlegi, eo quod nihil aliud ex iis perspicere po<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tui, quam vanam esse omnem spem meam, et mihi, licet quam citissime <rs type="place">Basileam</rs> rever<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/><pb facs="1037851" n="2"/>tenti, vix potestatem fore tua ibidem fruendi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentia; quanquam igitur exigua mihi spes re<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>linquatur te videndi, animum tamen non omnino despondeo, cum firmiter credam, te conditio<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>nem oblatam <choice><sic>detrectarum</sic><corr>detrecturum</corr></choice>, si bene perpenderis rationes illas, ob quas mihi in tenebris <rs type="place">Hin<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>delbanckianis</rs> vitam non esse ferendam judicasti, eadem enim ne <rs type="place">Rollam</rs> abeas suadent; ad
<lb/>majora certe tibi quoque aspirandum est, quam ad p<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dagogi vices in loco aliquo obscuro per
<lb/>tres aut plures annos obeundas, dico per tres annos, tamdiu enim aut diutius tibi expectan<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>dum esset, donec cum isto <rs type="person">juvene</rs> iter facere posses, et falleris profecto vehementer, si pu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tas Dominam <rs type="person"><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Wattenw<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>l</rs> <abbr>D.</abbr> Colonelli <rs type="person">de Rosey</rs> <rs type="person">viduam</rs> <rs type="person">filium</rs> suum post semestre ad ex<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>teros missuram esse, quia ut audio maxime juvenis est et vix 12<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> annos habet, et si vel
<lb/>maxime quindecim aut sedecim annos haberet, dubitandum tamen esset, an tu ejus in
<lb/>itinere comes esse posses, solent quidem omnes Bernenses hoc ab initio promittere, sed qu<choice><orig><g ref="#an">ā</g></orig><reg>an</reg></choice><pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>do res in effectum est deducenda, facile ipsis est sub variis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>textibus promissa fallere
<lb/>et aliquem, si diutius manere nolit, parte etiam salarii defraudare. Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea quid <rs type="place">Rol<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> proficere possis, non video, pagus enim est <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> nemine fere habitatus nisi <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> rusticis,
<lb/>qui Sabaudica dialecto utuntur, nec ibi invenies literatos aut politicos, <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> quorum
<lb/>conversatione Gallicam linguam addiscere posses, et tibi in tali domo, in qua nullus est
<lb/>pater familias, eremitam agere necessum foret. Suadeo igitur tibi, ut hoc anno domi ma<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>neas, et studiis tuis graviter incumbere pergas, nullus enim dubito, te brevi tempore
<lb/>laborum tam laudabiliter exantlatorum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>mia reportaturum, Deumque tibi
<lb/>longe meliorem stationem monstraturum esse. Si tamen brevi tempore cum aliquo ju<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>vene itinerari posses, non repugnarem, ut ejusmodi conditiones susciperes; sed ut p<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dago<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>gum ageres et per plures annos intra privatos parietes delitesceres, non suaderem, opti<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>me igitur ages, si in statum rei quam accuratissime inquiras, nec conditionem istam susci<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>pias, nisi certissimum sit <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>quod tamen ego plane non credo<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> <rs type="person">juvenem</rs> hunc iter mox factu<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>rum esse. Ulterius de hisce rebus nunc ratiocinari non licet, animus enim mihi plane est
<lb/>irrequietus, quia mihi iter in <rs type="place">Galliam</rs> ob miseriam et contagiones, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ibi regnant,
<lb/>undique dissuadetur, proficiscar tamen his non obstantibus Deo volente circa festum 
<pb facs="1037852" n="3"/> 
<lb/><date>Pentecostes</date>, et circa finem <date>mensis Augusti</date>, ut spero, <rs type="place">Basileam</rs> rediturus sum, ubi fac ut
<lb/>te inveniam. Animum, ut suades, quantum licet exhilarare studeo, <date>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terita nocte</date>
<lb/>apud <rs type="person">Raillardum</rs> cubui, et non solum ex eo sed etiam ex <rs type="person">Schwartzio</rs> <rs type="place">Bern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> audivi,
<lb/>quantum tibi placeat consistorialitas. Problema propositum optime solvisti, et quin
<lb/>Anal<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>sis bene se habeat, non dubito.</p> <closer><salute>Vale, Amice optime, et me tuis co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odis inservire
<lb/>paratum esse crede.</salute><dateline> Dabam <rs type="place">Genev<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1710-05-26">26. Maji 1710.</date></dateline></closer>
</div>
